                      GoDaddy
                    </p>
                    <small data-registrar_name="godaddy" data-registrar="GoDaddy" class="tip registrar-tip">Click the button to connect to a GoDaddy account.</small>
                  </div>
                  <div class="control-right">
                    <a data-registrar_name="godaddy" class="add-registrar-button button is-stylish is-small">
                      <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fa fa-link"></i></span>
                      <span class="registrar-button-text" data-registrar="GoDaddy"></span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="control is-spaced">
